@node Description "Description"

PROGRAMM: EXEcutor V1.1 (short: EXE)
AUTHOR:   SMC of AbYsS
DATA:     May 1994
CLASS:    Freeware

Description:

        Be proud to get the latest version of 'Executor' (hehe).
        Normally this proramm makes no sense, coz it's only
        function is to execute a program.

        But if you use CLI often and you are sad about typing
        stupid name of demos or something else like
        'chil-fuck94.p17^tro.exe' than use Executor.
        Once installed in 'C:', type only 'EXE' and choose
        Name by Requester.
@endnode


@node History "History"


        History:

                V1.0 many bugs
                V1.1 I hope no bugs

@endnode

@node Requirements "Requirements"


        Requirements:

                Executor needs ASL.Library, so it only runs under
                Kick 2.0+ .
                Under ReqTools (I haven't included an interface, so
                use RTPatch or something else!) it looks more
                comfortable.

                If you use an 68040+ Processor it's faster, but:
                you won't recognize any difference (hehe!).
@endnode


@node Future "Future Ideas"



        Future Ideas:

                There is no sense to do another version of this.

@endnode

